      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're not a doctor but i'm just asking for general info. i read online that if you take smaller doses more frequently you can keep a steady level of the medicine in your system so the pain never really spikes. given that, wouldn't taking 400mg every 2 hours be a more effective way to manage it than waiting 6 hours for the next dose? it seems more logical for constant pain.",
