      "content": "but the packaging says you shouldn't take more than 1200mg in a day. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, i'll only be at 2400mg if i go for 12 hours straight, but does that really matter if the pain is that bad? i feel like if the pain is constant, the \"standard\" limit shouldn't really apply because my body needs more relief. can't i just push through and take it more often if it's helping me function?",
